<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Docs on 🛡️ Dragon Shell</title><link>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/</link><description>Recent content in Docs on 🛡️ Dragon Shell</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>pt</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 20:44:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>归档页面</title><link>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/archives/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 20:44:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/archives/</guid><description>&lt;p>你需要创建 &lt;code>content/archives/_index.md&lt;/code> 来启用归档页面。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="island mb-4 overflow-hidden not-prose">
 
 &lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>---
title: &amp;#34;Archives&amp;#34;
description: &amp;#34;...&amp;#34;
draft: false
icon: archive-box
cover:
 image: cover.jpg
---&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>如果你的 &lt;code>_index.md&lt;/code> 不在 &lt;code>content/archives/&lt;/code> 目录下面，那你可以给你的 &lt;code>_index.md&lt;/code> 的 frontmatter 添加 &lt;code>layout: archives&lt;/code> 来启用这一特性。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="island mb-4 overflow-hidden not-prose">
 
 &lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>---
title: &amp;#34;Archives&amp;#34;
description: &amp;#34;...&amp;#34;
draft: false
icon: archive-box
cover:
 image: cover.jpg
layout: archives
---&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>封面图</title><link>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/cover-images/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 13:34:56 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/cover-images/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="添加封面图">添加封面图&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="island mb-4 overflow-hidden not-prose">
 
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nn">---&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">title&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;your-post-title&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># ...&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">cover&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">example.jpg&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">alt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">xxx&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Optional&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nn">---&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h3 id="为作者添加作者头像">为作者添加作者头像&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="island mb-4 overflow-hidden not-prose">
 
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nn">---&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">title&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;author-name&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># ...&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">avatar&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">example-avatar.jpg&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">alt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Example Avatar&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">cover&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">example-background.jpg&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">alt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Example Background Image&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>配置图标</title><link>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/icons/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 13:24:23 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/pt/docs/icons/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="icons">Icons&lt;/h2>
&lt;h2 id="图标">图标&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>图标可以用在&lt;a href="https://rxluk.github.io/dragon-shell/docs/menu-config/">导航栏菜单&lt;/a>，或者&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/content-management/taxonomies/">分类页 / taxonomy pages&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>内置的图标存放于主题的 &lt;code>assets/icons&lt;/code> 目录下面，是 &lt;a href="https://heroicons.com/">heroicons&lt;/a> 的一部分。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="添加更多图标">添加更多图标&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>你可以添加更多 svg 图标（不局限于 heroicons）到你的站点的 &lt;code>assets/icons&lt;/code> 目录下面，来扩展或者覆盖可用的图标。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>图标也可以放在 &lt;code>assets/icons&lt;/code> 下面的子文件夹中，例如，如果图标 &lt;code>assets/icons/my-icons/my-icon.svg&lt;/code> 存在，那么你可以使用 &lt;code>my-icons/my-icon&lt;/code> 来引用你的图标。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>查看 &lt;code>partials/icon.html&lt;/code> 了解更多。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>